section_summary: The text is a speech given by Mr. Marzouq Al-Hubaini, congratulating Mr. Mohammed Barak Al-Mutair on his election as the President of the National Assembly. Al-Hubaini emphasizes the importance of unity and working together for the benefit of Kuwait. He acknowledges the support of the Kuwaiti people and their expectations for development and improvement in the country. Al-Hubaini stresses that success should be measured by the progress made for Kuwait and its people. The text also includes a reference to the legislative session and its agenda.
